data.description: Great home waiting your finishing touches. With a little TLC, this home has great potential. Seller has installed new Windows and a New Roof to make this an investor's dream or a Buyer that doesn't mind a little work. Updated bath with Jacuzzi tub and 5-head shower with headed floors. Upstairs is ready for 2 bedrooms and a 1/2 bath rough-in needs to be framed out, plus room for a 3rd bedroom upstairs too.  Outside is a fully fenced backyard and oversized 2+ car garage with workshop area. Cash or Conventional Buyers only!
